-----------
 * Using pax tar archive format for storing backup data to support Unicode
   and long file names.


Version 0.3
-----------
 * Fully rewritten and rethought code and configuration file format.
 * This version supports Python 3+ only.


Version 0.2
-----------
 * New configuration file option - hash_size.
 * Fixed a bug due to which backup restoring failed when one of backups was
   corrupted.
 * A few small fixes.


Version 0.1
